{
  "stem": "2581.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And but when I-- when I-- you asked me about the factory, the-- my business in Poland.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Originally, I had bought a shop, a clothing factory, in Brooklyn.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "How I bought it, how I did it, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I did it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were employing 100 people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And things started to go well for us till the import started from Eastern Europe.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that put me out of business.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And if you can't lick them, you have to join them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I had to make a living.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the situation came up where we were able to do some business to bring in some garments from Eastern Europe.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It started with Poland, then Hungary, Romania, Bulgaria, Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I did it for 17 years.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Tell me about that incident with the matzah.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think that [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, there were many incidents in Poland where I came across anti-Semitic statements, where people would say, oh, I didn't mean anything.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We just talk here like that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had come across some very, very righteous Poles.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I have heard-- and I had a book about an organization called [INAUDIBLE], that they were purely dedicated to save Jews.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I also know about them playing music, having a merry-go-round, and singing songs at the time when the Warsaw ghetto was burning, saying that it's only Jews that are burning there.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I, in my travels, had different kinds-- all kinds of experiences, positive and negative.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I have been to a Hungarian cathedral where I heard the priest saying in Hungarian-- and I do understand Hungarian-- don't believe the Jew, because the Jew lies.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I-- I have went and gone to Polish masses, to cathedrals, and hear what is being said.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
